  "title": "Warehouse Operator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Handle physical goods (electronic components), picking, packing and receiving &amp; data entry.</li>\n  <li>Participate in Annual Stock-take.</li>\n  <li>To assist in other warehousing activities when necessary.</li>\n  <li>To maintain safe and clean work environment.</li>\n  <li>Any other ad-hoc duties.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preferably 1-year exp in warehousing or store inventory.</li>\n  <li>Must have a valid forklift license</li>\n  <li>Preferably familiar with handheld scanner &amp; computerized warehouse system</li>\n  <li>Preferably have equipment maintenance and record-keeping knowledge</li>\n  <li>Able to handle physical work and manual carton lifting</li>\n  <li>Basic computer skills</li>\n</ul>",
